    <item>
      <title>英国经济 2022 年增长超出此前预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/uk-economy-s-2022-growth-was-more-than-previously-estimated</link>
      <description><![CDATA[最新数据显示，英国经济在 2022 年抵御两位数通胀和政治动荡的影响比最初预想的要好，产出增长速度加快。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/uk-economy-s-2022-growth-was-more-than-previously-estimated</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 06:17:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈利法克斯称英国房价自一月份以来涨幅最大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/uk-house-prices-rise-the-quickest-since-january-halifax-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国最大的抵押贷款机构之一表示，英国房价在三个月的低迷之后恢复增长，以自一月份以来的最快速度上涨，进一步表明市场正在应对利率上升的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/uk-house-prices-rise-the-quickest-since-january-halifax-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 06:11:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国敦促官员停止玩“扔鸡蛋”纸牌游戏</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/china-urges-officials-to-stop-playing-throwing-eggs-card-game</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国呼吁官员停止玩一种广受欢迎的扑克游戏，因为这影响了他们的工作，这一问题暗示了国家主席习近平长期以来对全国数百万公务员的不满。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/china-urges-officials-to-stop-playing-throwing-eggs-card-game</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 05:38:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
