    <item>
      <title>拉贾帕克萨家族竞选总统，斯里兰卡家族回归</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/sri-lanka-party-names-rajapaksa-scion-as-presidential-candidate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[下个月，强大的拉贾帕克萨家族的一名后裔将参加斯里兰卡总统大选。两年多前，他的民粹主义叔叔领导斯里兰卡陷入了有史以来最严重的经济危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/sri-lanka-party-names-rajapaksa-scion-as-presidential-candidate</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 03:41:40 GMT</pubDate>
